				<td colspan="2"><span>i upgraded from a p3-500 360meg, 32 meg vid card to a p4 2.5 512 meg, 128mo vid card about 2 months ago
<br />

<br />
forget ae kite, your system wont take it. it might work well for a bit til yuor system get a brainfart to recalculate the graphics ( in wich case you will splat)
<br />

<br />
you should be able to use other type of kiting tho, depending on wich zone you go.
<br />

<br />
on my old fart comp, in option ( before you log in game) i turned graphics to low quality, had only 3-4 luclin model on, no light texturing, most of those option in fact were at low.
<br />

<br />
in game, max max clip plane i could set was 30% ( except in ldon go figure) had also sky off, everything you can think of off ( journal, log, lots of battle spam off) to reduce the influx of data between you and the server. 
<br />

<br />
lastly, zone with lots of trees and/or lots of texturing ( poi is one) will be extremely difficult to deal with. 
<br />

<br />
like i said, i was able to chant kite usually without any problem, and in low lag zone i could swarm kite. 
<br />

<br />
hope this help a bit</span></td>
